#: .\food.json
msgid "ketchup soup"
msgid_plural "ketchup soups"
msgstr[0] "番茄醬湯"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'ketchup soup'}
#: .\food.json
msgid "It smells of tomatoes, but it's ketchup."
msgstr "聞起來像番茄，但其實是番茄醬。"

#: .\food.json
msgid "hotdog soup"
msgid_plural "hotdog soups"
msgstr[0] "熱狗湯"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'hotdog soup'}
#: .\food.json
msgid ""
"It smells of Hot dog, but it's just ketchup and sausage. quite filling."
msgstr "聞起來像熱狗，但只是番茄醬和香腸。相當管飽。"

#: .\food.json
msgid "glassed eggs"
msgid_plural "glassed eggss"
msgstr[0] "玻璃化雞蛋"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'glassed eggs'}
#: .\food.json
msgid "Eggs water glassed using lime water, they will last forever."
msgstr "使用石灰水進行玻璃化處理的雞蛋，可永久保存。"

#: .\food.json
msgid "omelette"
msgid_plural "omelettes"
msgstr[0] "煎蛋卷"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'omelette'}
#: .\food.json
msgid "Delicious seasoned cuisine, made from beaten eggs."
msgstr "美味的調味菜餚，由打散的雞蛋製成。"

#: .\food.json
msgid "deluxe omelettes"
msgid_plural "deluxe omelettess"
msgstr[0] "豪華煎蛋卷"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'deluxe omelettes'}
#: .\food.json
msgid ""
"Delicious seasoned cuisine, made from beaten eggs with delicious melting "
"cheese filling inside."
msgstr "美味的調味菜餚，由打散的雞蛋製成，內含美味融化的芝士餡料。"

#: .\food.json
msgid "Fruity French toast"
msgid_plural "Fruity French toasts"
msgstr[0] "水果法式吐司"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Fruity French toast'}
#: .\food.json
msgid ""
"Also known as poor knight, this delicious toast is made from soft egg-soaked"
" bread fried on a flat metal surface with fruit and sweets added."
msgstr "亦稱窮騎士吐司，這道美味吐司由浸透蛋液的軟麵包在平金屬面上煎制而成，並添加了水果和甜點。"

#: .\food.json
msgid "Garlic bread"
msgid_plural "Garlic breads"
msgstr[0] "蒜香麵包"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Garlic bread'}
#: .\food.json
msgid ""
"This delicious toast is made from soft butter and crushed garlic infused "
"into the toast, fried on a flat metal surface with seasoning added. Approved"
" by Vampire hunters."
msgstr "這道美味吐司由軟黃油和碾碎的大蒜融入麵包中，在平金屬面上煎制並添加調味料。獲吸血鬼獵人認可。"

#: .\modinfo.json
msgid "Culinary Days Ahead"
msgstr "未來烹飪時代"

#. ~ Description for Culinary Days Ahead
#: .\modinfo.json
msgid "Surviving the dragon way"
msgstr "以龍之道求生"
